   ACTION INDUSTRIES Inc. (Pittsburgh) -- Ernest S. Berez, 65
years old, will retire as chairman of this promotional
merchandise marketer, effective July 31, but remain a
director. Mr. Berez previously said he would retire as chief
executive officer, to be succeeded by R. Craig Kirsch,
Action's 43-year-old president. The board is expected to
select a new chairman at its July meeting.
